{"tid":2378848,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–化療效果參差的其中一道原因","createTime":"2021-01-24T22:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T02:02:16.000Z","uid":38861,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b85db9116875292ef233bb2f040ac657584431d","tid":2378848,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"化療殺滅癌細胞的效率非常參差，有些情況更反而會導致癌細胞加速生長，究竟為何會這樣?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCZiraQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCZiraQ.jpg&h=aa8f101e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）使用化療藥物過後，某些癌細胞的確是會歸西死亡。<br />\n而細胞死亡的方式有好幾種，其中兩種為Apoptosis及Necrosis。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ex0dZvS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fex0dZvS.png&h=c2a8792e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖中所見，進行Apoptosis的細胞會呈完整球狀，屍體相對的體積較大。<br />\n而進行Necrosis的細胞則會分成為不規則的碎塊，體積亦較細。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）形象化來說，Apoptosis就是曲奇餅，而Necrosis就是曲奇餅碎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2trz4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2trz4f.jpg&h=c468ace8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）癌細胞被化療藥物殺死後，若進行Necrosis，鄰近沒受化療影響的癌細胞便會啟動一道名為Macropinocytosis的機制，將死亡的細胞吞噬，作營養供用使自己繼續成長，抵禦化療藥物所帶來的困境。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiE2SQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiE2SQY.jpg&h=f35f74b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但細胞進行Apoptosis的話，因屍體體積過大，鄰近的細胞便不能把其吞噬。<br />\n<br />\n並不是所有癌細胞亦能懂得施展Macropinocytosis，而整個機制學界亦在模索之中，只知道某些基因如PI3K或Ras進行突變的話，Macropinocytosis發生的機率亦會較大。<br />\n<br />\n若能掌握整套機制及研發藥物制止Macropinocytosis的發生，並在化療藥物其間同時使用，便能壓抑癌細胞吞噬死亡細胞的機制，大大增加化療的效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCLCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=1275307d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCLCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=56717104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-14928-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41467-020-14928-3&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCLCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=327c766e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-14928-3</a>"},{"pid":"8555fdc4646528520b95c46df27271ea408e1f70","tid":2378848,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T22:36:02.000Z","msg":"樓主咁早起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79d076f8dcade8657aa011a9cccaa6d2a462428","tid":2378848,"uid":258356,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T22:55:14.000Z","msg":"傳說Keto diet / 斷食可以trigger身體細胞自噬，從而消滅癌細胞<br />\n點解好似研究唔太多，同埋入唔到主流醫學？"},{"pid":"ad54b78fde809cbc0a4ba69f8c197fb3eaaa9644","tid":2378848,"uid":82658,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T23:00:46.000Z","msg":"其實apoptosis 係細胞自行programmed 嘅死亡<br />\n中間嘅過程唔單止 淨係&quot;我死啦&quot; <br />\n而係同周圍附近講 &quot;喂！大家！我死啦！叫清道夫收垃圾呀喂！！&quot; 之後先死<br />\n死咗之後會有 macrophages 同其他唔同嘅白血球去到個個位 用個垃圾袋包住佢 等佢唔會周圍散開咁臭 即係啲垃圾唔會搞到其他地方<br />\n<br />\n但necrosis 係 比黑狗打死 （外來因素整死）<br />\n冇叫啲白血球收屍同清理地方<br />\n死咗之後爛到一舊舊咁 啲垃圾周圍飛 污染埋周圍<br />\n你可以當啲爛咗嘅癌細胞係種子 揾個垃圾袋包住就唔發芽 冇包住就可能到邊就落地生根咁<br />\n<br />\n新一代抗癌係target 係 trigger apoptosis, programmed cell death 為其中一個大方向"},{"pid":"5ae3c21eec4daabfa9c371cfa263e530228e8f06","tid":2378848,"uid":82658,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d79d076f8dcade8657aa011a9cccaa6d2a462428","tid":2378848,"uid":258356,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T22:55:14.000Z","msg":"傳說Keto diet / 斷食可以trigger身體細胞自噬，從而消滅癌細胞<br />\n點解好似研究唔太多，同埋入唔到主流醫學？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T23:11:17.000Z","msg":"Keto diet 唔講住 要一個cancer patient 進行keto 好risky 唔講中間有機可能酮酸中毒令免疫力下降同其他併發症<br />\n由斷食trigger apoptosis 到 食晒cancer cell 中間太多過程 <br />\n身體入面好多機能唔係input a 就出 b <br />\n可能係 b c d e <br />\n到食cancer cell 可能已經係 l m n o嘅過程<br />\n唔係100％唔係 而家好難去統計明確嘅因果<br />\n<br />\n加上又要確保patients 係斷食期間 唔會唔夠營養而導致免疫力下降 <br />\n所以除非個patients 係過重 如果唔係都唔建議斷食<br />\n過重減肥同斷食又係兩回事"},{"pid":"6b4f883c02133c23a2317a42cfa19d12e4a37e75","tid":2378848,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cfb6a1fcca89cccff5e4a421d5b6330935ba82","tid":2378848,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"化療根本就係過時嘅土法嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早要將標靶藥納入第一線資助藥物啦"},{"pid":"b21c435a35f8de30e0f4222d2283a9fdc2633f95","tid":2378848,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9cfb6a1fcca89cccff5e4a421d5b6330935ba82","tid":2378848,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"化療根本就係過時嘅土法嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早要將標靶藥納入第一線資助藥物啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"藥廠霸權，無辧去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c114e4c971db7cc5eaf49c91f4687aa64a2c80a","tid":2378848,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8555fdc4646528520b95c46df27271ea408e1f70","tid":2378848,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T22:36:02.000Z","msg":"樓主咁早起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"每次都有人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2108ca9372aa06855c3b3efdf85460d5b4c20036","tid":2378848,"uid":239486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"dc1ae051f41edb0b7e2c6708ebb439a737188efa","tid":2378848,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c114e4c971db7cc5eaf49c91f4687aa64a2c80a","tid":2378848,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8555fdc4646528520b95c46df27271ea408e1f70","tid":2378848,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T22:36:02.000Z","msg":"樓主咁早起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"每次都有人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"新讀lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解咁問嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea12a31ac31f2c5f7e